&lt;p&gt;In Sanskrit, there are two words: &lt;em&gt;Sanyasa&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Tyaga&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
People in the English-speaking world think both mean renunciation.&lt;br&gt;
They are related but not the same.&lt;br&gt;
